skins.shipDescription: Fletcher-class destroyer - Aulick, Hull Number DD-569!
skins.selfIntroduction: I'm Aulick of the Little Beavers! I was mainly tasked with air rescues. I'm not as strong as the captain, but I'll be more than satisfied as long as you let me fight till the end!
skins.acquisition: Yaaay! It's so great to meet you, Commander! Just call me Aulick! ... What was that? I said Aulick! My name is Aulick!
skins.details: Don't forget to keep your gear in working order, Commander!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Commander, won't you take Aulick out to play~?
skins.secretaryIdle2: Aulick loves hanging out with all the other Little Beavers!
skins.secretaryIdle3: Ah, Aulick likes the Commander too, of course!
skins.secretaryTouch: Aren't I so soft and squishy?
